description:
Artist Neisha Neshae and Producer Dre Butterz join the ladies of Lip Service this week and discuss gifts for the holidays, forgivable reasons for cheating, dealing with people who stay on their phones, and much more! Neisha even breaks down why men aren't supposed to nut when having sex. Enjoy!
